  "body": "<!--\r\nNeed help?\r\nRefer to our contributing guidelines for additional information about making a good issue:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/.github/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nThere are multiple places where the EIP 1967 constants are used and they are defined inline multiple times. We should deduplicate the values.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nWe should hardcode the constants into `Constants.sol` and then also have unit tests that the values are correct and also import the values from the constants library into all the places where they are used.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
